---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="AutoPacker | Expert IT Packaging & Deployment">
    <!-- Animated Gradient Orb -->
    <div class="absolute left-0 right-0 top-20 -z-10 m-auto h-[310px] w-[310px] rounded-full bg-blue-600/20 dark:bg-blue-500/20 opacity-20 blur-[100px] animate-pulse"></div>

    <!-- 1. The Pain/Pivot Section -->
    <section class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16 sm:mb-24 md:mb-32">
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-800 to-slate-600 dark:from-slate-100 dark:to-slate-400 pb-4 transition-colors duration-300 hover:from-blue-600">
            Packaging shouldn't be the bottleneck.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-4 transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-slate-700 dark:hover:text-slate-200">
            Every failed software deployment is a drain on resources. Whether migrating to the cloud, managing legacy infrastructure, or simply keeping pace with updates, poorly packaged applications create a cascade of helpdesk tickets, frustrate users, and halt productivity. We are your dedicated remote packaging partner.
        </p>
    </section>

    <!-- 2. The Tech Stack Grid -->
    <section class="mb-16 sm:mb-24 md:mb-32">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:gap-6 lg:gap-8">
            
            <div class="p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 bg-white/50 dark:bg-slate-900/50 transition-shadow duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-blue-500/20 dark:hover:shadow-blue-500/15">
                <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 mb-2 md:mb-3 transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400">Intune & Modern Workplace</h3>
                <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-slate-700 dark:hover:text-slate-300">Full adoption of the cloud model. We specialize in `.intunewin` preparation, rigorous testing on Windows 10/11, Autopilot application deployments, and proactive management.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 bg-white/50 dark:bg-slate-900/50 transition-shadow duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-blue-500/20 dark:hover:shadow-blue-500/15">
                <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 mb-2 md:mb-3 transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400">SCCM / MECM Mastery</h3>
                <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-slate-700 dark:hover:text-slate-300">Go beyond simple deployments with end-to-end application lifecycle management. We handle complex task sequences, dependency chains, supersedence, and phased rollouts.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 bg-white/50 dark:bg-slate-900/50 transition-shadow duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-cyan-500/20 dark:hover:shadow-cyan-400/15">
                <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 mb-2 md:mb-3 transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-cyan-600 dark:hover:text-cyan-400">Advanced Repackaging</h3>
                <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-slate-700 dark:hover:text-slate-300">True expertise in MSI, MSIX, and App-V using industry-standard tools like InstallShield and Master Packager. We craft robust, silent installations with complex PowerShell wrappers.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 bg-white/50 dark:bg-slate-900/50 transition-shadow duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-cyan-500/20 dark:hover:shadow-cyan-400/15">
                <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 mb-2 md:mb-3 transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-cyan-600 dark:hover:text-cyan-400">Apple Enterprise & Jamf</h3>
                <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-slate-700 dark:hover:text-slate-300">Bring the same level of enterprise control to your Mac fleet. Deep Jamf Pro and Jamf Composer expertise for custom PKG/DMG repackaging, pre/post-install scripting.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why Us? Section -->
    <section class="mb-16 sm:mb-24 md:mb-32 bg-slate-100/80 dark:bg-slate-900/50 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 lg:p-12 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 transition-colors duration-300 hover:bg-slate-100/95 dark:hover:bg-slate-900/70">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="md:col-span-1 text-center md:text-left">
                <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400">Why Us?</h2>
                <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-semibold mt-1">Experience meets Methodology</p>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-2 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-400 text-base sm:text-lg transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-slate-800 dark:hover:text-slate-300">
                <p>
                    With over 15 years dedicated exclusively to application packaging and enterprise deployments, we've seen every edge case. We deliver partnerships focused on long-term reliability and streamlined management.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 3. The Process Timeline -->
    <section class="mb-16 sm:mb-24 md:mb-32">
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            <div class="space-y-12 md:space-y-16">
                <!-- Step 1 -->
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4 md:gap-6 group">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                        <span class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl font-black text-slate-300 dark:text-slate-700/80 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-blue-400/60 dark:group-hover:text-blue-500/60">01</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 mt-1 md:mt-2">
                        <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-blue-600 dark:group-hover:text-blue-400">The Handoff</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mt-2 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-slate-700 dark:group-hover:text-slate-300">Provide the source media and requirements. We establish a discovery call to confirm scope and define success criteria.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Step 2 -->
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4 md:gap-6 group">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                        <span class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl font-black text-slate-300 dark:text-slate-700/80 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-blue-400/60 dark:group-hover:text-blue-500/60">02</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 mt-1 md:mt-2">
                        <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-blue-600 dark:group-hover:text-blue-400">The Build</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mt-2 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-slate-700 dark:group-hover:text-slate-300">Your application is expertly repackaged for a silent, zero-touch installation. Work performed in isolated lab adhering to best practices.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Step 3 -->
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4 md:gap-6 group">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                        <span class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl font-black text-slate-300 dark:text-slate-700/80 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-blue-400/60 dark:group-hover:text-blue-500/60">03</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 mt-1 md:mt-2">
                        <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-blue-600 dark:group-hover:text-blue-400">The Delivery</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mt-2 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-slate-700 dark:group-hover:text-slate-300">You receive thoroughly tested MSI, MSIX, or PKG with comprehensive documentation for immediate deployment.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 4. Footer/CTA -->
    <footer class="text-center mt-24 pb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-blue-600">Ready to clear your packaging backlog?</h2>
        <a href="mailto:example@example.com" 
           class="inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 dark:from-blue-500 dark:to-cyan-400 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 sm:py-4 sm:px-10 rounded-lg text-base sm:text-lg
                  shadow-lg shadow-blue-600/20 dark:shadow-blue-500/20 
                  hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-cyan-500/30 dark:hover:shadow-cyan-400/30
                  transition-shadow duration-300
                  active:opacity-90
                  touch-target">
            Let's Talk Deployment
        </a>
        <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-500 font-mono mt-10 sm:mt-12 tracking-wider transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-slate-600 dark:hover:text-slate-400">>_ Hosted on Azure. Provisioned with Terraform.</p>
    </footer>
</Layout>
